OL,3,C'They've been forgotten': Parents at
OL,4,CRAAC school worry for children's exams
OL,6,FSix months following the partial
OL,7,Fclosure of a Durham school found to
OL,8,Fhave RAAC, pupils say they feel
OL,9,Fthey've been forgotten by the
OL,10,FGovernment.
OL,12,FSt Leonard's Catholic School in
OL,13,FDurham, which has 1,490 pupils, moved
OL,14,Fmost of its learning online when RAAC
OL,15,Fwas found in several buildings in
OL,16,FSeptember last year.
OL,18,FWhile all pupils have returned to in-
OL,19,Fperson learning, 40% are in new
OL,20,Ftemporary accommodation stationed on
OL,21,Fthe sports field and playground.
