OL,3,C'They've been forgotten': Parents at
OL,4,CRAAC school worry for children's exams
OL,6,FShadow Education Secretary Bridget
OL,7,FPhillipson said she is deeply
OL,8,Fconcerned impact the partial closure
OL,9,Fof school is having on students and
OL,10,Ftheir life chances, when visiting the
OL,11,Fschool on Friday 1 March.
OL,13,FThe Houghton and Sunderland South MP
OL,14,Fsays she does not believe the
OL,15,Fgovernment are reacting adequately.
OL,17,FSpeaking to ITV Tyne Tees, she said:
OL,18,F"I'm glad that all children are now
OL,19,Fback on site in temporary
OL,20,Faccommodation but this has been months
OL,21,Fand months of disruption.
