OL,3,C'They've been forgotten': Parents at
OL,4,CRAAC school worry for children's exams
OL,6,F"It's just not good enough and it's
OL,7,Fshameful that Conservative ministers
OL,8,Fdid not give a great priority to these
OL,9,Fstudents in the North East and in
OL,10,Fparticular at St Leonards."
OL,12,FThe Bishop Wilkinson Catholic
OL,13,FEducation Trust (BWCET), which runs
OL,14,Fthe school, applied to be allowed to
OL,15,Fuse centre-assessed grades, as
OL,16,Fhappened during lockdown when teachers
OL,17,Fgraded their own pupils.
