OL,3,C'They've been forgotten': Parents at
OL,4,CRAAC school worry for children's exams
OL,6,FThis request was rejected by the exam
OL,7,Fregulator Ofqual, leaving parents and
OL,8,Fpupils concerned they would be
OL,9,Fdisadvantaged by the disruption.
OL,11,FA Department for Education
OL,12,Fspokesperson said: "The safety of
OL,13,Fstaff and pupils is paramount, and we
OL,14,Fhave been working at pace with
OL,15,Fschools, including St Leonards, to
OL,16,Fidentify and confirm the removal route
OL,17,Fof RAAC to support them to minimise
OL,18,Fdisruption to pupils' education.
