OL,6,F"Alongside Ofqual we have worked with
OL,7,Fawarding organisations to help
OL,8,Ffacilitate discussions with affected
OL,9,Fschools.
OL,11,F"We have asked awarding organisations
OL,12,Fto, where possible, agree longer
OL,13,Fextensions for coursework and non-
OL,14,Fexamined assessment so that schools
OL,15,Fhave as much time as possible to
OL,16,Fcomplete this important part of
OL,17,Fpupils' learning and qualifications."
